text: The SEAT Toledo is a car produced by SEAT in four generations from 1991 to 2019. == First generation (1991–1999) == === Engines === ==== Petrol ==== * 1.6 53 kW (72 hp), 55 kW (75 hp) and 74 kW (100 hp) * 1.8 66 kW (90 hp) * 1.8 16V 94 kW (128 hp) * 2.0 85 kW (115 hp) * 2.0 16V 110 kW (150 hp) ==== Diesel ==== * 1.9 D 47 kW (64 hp) and 50 kW (68 hp) * 1.9 TD 55 kW (75 hp) * 1.9 TDI 66 kW (90 hp) and 81 kW (110 hp) == Second generation (1999–2004) == === Engines === ==== Petrol ==== * 1.4 16V 55 kW (75 hp) * 1.6 74 kW (100 hp) * 1.6 16V 77 kW (105 hp) * 1.8 20V 92 kW (125 hp) * 1.8 20V Turbo 132 kW (180 hp) * 2.3 VR5 110 kW (150 hp) and 125 kW (170 hp) ==== Diesel ==== * 1.9 TDI 66 kW (90 hp), 81 kW (110 hp), 96 kW (130 hp) and 110 kW (150 hp) == Third generation (2004–2009) == === Engines === ==== Petrol ==== * 1.4 63 kW (86 hp) * 1.6 75 kW (102 hp) * 1.8 TSI 118 kW (160 hp) * 2.0 FSI 110 kW (150 hp) * 2.0 TSI 147 kW (200 hp) ==== Diesel ==== * 1.9 TDI 77 kW (104 hp) * 2.0 TDI 100 kW (136 hp), 103 kW (140 hp) and 125 kW (170 hp) == Fourth generation (2013-2019) == === Engines === ==== Petrol ==== * 1.2 TSI 63 kW (86, 105 hp) * 1.4 TSI 75 kW (122 hp) ==== Diesel ==== * 1.6 TDI 77 kW (90, 105 hp) Toledo Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
